<div class="landing container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col left-panel">
            <h1 class="landing-heading my-4"> A good heading... </h1>

            <p> World Health Organization (WHO) and its partners have developed a tool with a list of benchmarks and corresponding actions that can be applied to increase the performance of countries in emergency preparedness through the development and implementation of a National Action Plan for Health Security (NAPHS). </p>

            <p> Use this tool to get help with creating a draft plan, explore best practices in the reference library, or browse the benchmarks. </p>

            <%= form_tag('/country_select', data: { controller: "country_selection" }) do %>
              <div class="input-group">
                <%= select_tag "country", options_from_collection_for_select(@countries, 'name', 'name'), class: "custom-select", data: { target: "country_selection.selectedCountry" } %>
                <div class="input-group-append">
                  <%= button_tag "Get Started", type: :button, data: { action: "country_selection#select" }, class: "btn text-white bg-green" %>
                </div>
              </div>

              <%= select_tag "assessment_type", options_from_collection_for_select([], 'assessment_type', 'assessment_type'), data: { target: "country_selection.assessmentTypes" } %>
              <%= hidden_field_tag "countries_and_assessments", value: @selectables.to_json, data: { target: "country_selection.selectables" } %>
            <% end %>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
